Editing:
C   -- delete to EOL + insert mode
cc  -- change line
ciX -- change inner
       w: word
       ": quoted string
       (: parented string
       t: tagged body <tag>
n G -- goto line n
"+y -- yank to system clipboard
"+p -- paste from system clipboard
V   -- visual line

Folding:
zo -- open fold (right arrow)
zc -- close fold
za -- toggle fold
zm -- close all folds one level (more)
zr -- open all folds one level (reduce)

Rails Navigation:
gf     -- springt zum Symbol under cursor
CTRL-^ -- springt zurück
:A     -- alternate file, i.A. Testfile
:R     -- related file, Kontext-abhängig (z.B. Controller Action -> View)

Completion:
CTRL-p        -- complete word
CTRL-x CTRL-l -- complete whole line, e.g. for require statements

Deletion:
diX -- delete inner
       w: word
       p: paragraph
       ": quoted string
       (: parented string
       t: tagged string
daX -- delete all, like inner but includes delimiter
yiX -- yank inner
yaX -- yank all

Tab Navigation:
:tabnew
:tabclose
CTRL-PageUp / CTRL-PageDown

Window Navigation:
:vsplit -> CTRL-w v -- vertical split
:vnew               -- vertical split new
CTRL-W Arrow	    -- springt zwischen Windows

Nerdcommenter:
[count]<leader>c<space> -- toggle comment

vim-matchit:
% -- bounce from do to end, etc.

vim-surround:
csXY -- change surrounding X to Y

easygrep:
<leader>vr -- replace occurances of word under cursor or visual block
